{"id":277334,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/自曲新闻-连霍高速一桥梁因货车爆炸坍塌/","date":"2013-02-01T06:22:04Z","modified":"2014-12-31T07:15:49Z","title":"自曲新闻 | 连霍高速一桥梁因货车爆炸坍塌","content":"\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 25%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-277334 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/0201连霍.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/0201连霍-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/0201连霍-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/0201连霍-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKKJL2600AN0001.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKKJL2600AN0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKKJL2600AN0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKKJL2600AN0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKO1NS700AN0001.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKO1NS700AN0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKO1NS700AN0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/8MKO1NS700AN0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl>\n\t\t\t<br style='clear: both' />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>河南，中国——2月1日9:30左右，连霍高速741km+600m（三门峡段）南半幅一桥梁发生坍塌，目击者称是主干桥坍塌，还有几辆车掉落，目前伤亡情况仍不清楚。</p>\n<p>大河网报道称，一辆装载爆炸品的货车自西向东行至义昌大桥时，突然发生爆炸，导致大桥南半幅被炸毁，北半幅桥板松动，目前，爆炸已造成连霍高速双向断行，人员伤亡情况正在核实中，所载爆炸品到底是鞭炮还是其他物品尚不清楚。</p>\n<p>更新：媒体证实2月1日上午九点连霍高速渑池段服务区附近一辆载满烟花爆竹的货车发生爆炸，引起桥面断裂，事故造成26人死亡。FMN</p>\n<p>现场<a href=\"http://www.yixia.com/show/DEutGneWS0Ut1H3V.htm\" target=\"_blank\">救援视频</a></p>\n<p>来源：自曲新闻</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,8779],"tags":[22097,14334,26567,22079,22078,28582,9746]}